{% embed "modules/notification/views/layouts/htmlv2.twig" %}

    {% block title %}
        {{ t('mail.user_welcome.title', title) | raw }}
    {% endblock %}

    {% block headerimage %}
        {{ base64_image('@notification-assets/images/headers/blue_7.jpg') | raw }}
    {% endblock %}

    {% block content %}

        <p>
            {{ t('mail.welcome.p1',
            'Welcome to KidUp!
                A world of knowledge, love and dozens of unused children equipment. {rent_link} something now or rent you {rent_out_link}.', {
                'rent_link': '<a href="' ~ rent_url ~ '" target="_blank">' ~ t('mail.links.rent_uppercase', 'Rent') ~ '</a>',
                'rent_out_link': '<a href="' ~ rent_out_url ~ '" target="_blank">' ~ t('mail.links.equipment_out', 'equipment out') ~ '</a>'
            }) | raw }}
        </p>

        <p>Have you had the chance to fill out your <a href="#">profile</a> yet? If you do, other parents will have the chance to get to know you a little better, and it is easier to trust your KidUp-persona.</p>

        <p>You could also connect your account to the <a href="#">social media</a>, or <a href="#">share</a> the lovely story of you becoming a part of KidUp?</p>

        <p>If you have questions, feedback or just wants to chat feel free to contact me - Philip, in the <a href="#">app</a>. Read the FAQ or send me an email.</p>

        <p>Have an nice day, and yet again, welcome.</p>

        <p>Philip & KidUp</p>

    {% endblock %}

{% endembed %}